{"tid":115741,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶貨扮上等貨","createTime":"2017-02-10T18:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T12:15:49.000Z","uid":52516,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc16129bc269b792e2e3a6881c85220ac9fa7d63","tid":115741,"uid":52516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/11/024131_786994416811f30528e512320a692e8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F11%2F024131_786994416811f30528e512320a692e8d.jpg&h=26e1c45c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信大家間唔中碌下Facebook 都會見到呢個網站既贊助廣告 <br />\n小弟唔係打手亦唔係比佢地呃過 只係覺得佢地用淘貨賣貴成三倍口"},{"pid":"3b141358ed7a51d1c27a50985c690cffd1385422","tid":115741,"uid":52516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T18:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/11/024131_786994416811f30528e512320a692e8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F11%2F024131_786994416811f30528e512320a692e8d.jpg&h=26e1c45c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信大家間唔中碌下Facebook 都會見到呢個網站既贊助廣告 <br />\n小弟唔係打手亦唔係比佢地呃過 只係覺得佢地用淘貨賣貴成三倍呢件事好老戇鳩 <br />\n例子：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/11/024935_5db43d379020aa8910179c71d794adc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F11%2F024935_5db43d379020aa8910179c71d794adc8.jpg&h=8fdd0cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27mvcY7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27mvcY7.jpg&h=ae4f38da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原價百令蚊一條 佢地就賣成三百蚊條 貴成足足三倍<br />\n當然明買明賣 一個願打一個願捱 我都只係多事下討論下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"0e579fbc46cb58914bb81a3405b4b29b496af115","tid":115741,"uid":3268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2