/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我都幾肯定係淘寶貨 因為呢個鬼仔都幫好多唔同樣既淘寶衫做model 假如假off white <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩叫假如假off white<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如假off white</span> 打錯字對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbc0256fc18072bf9271adb2d6bbdd13dba799b","tid":115741,"uid":52516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:30:03.000Z","msg":"其實我一早已經講左只係討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我無話要打擊佢地做生意無叫大家去唱衰or抵制佢地<br />\n我一早都講左一個願打一個願挨 有人肯買唔到我理<br />\n我只係講出黎提醒下大家唔好見呢o的o係Facebook 有贊助廣告既店鋪其實都係賣淘寶貨 等大家唔好食炒價姐 <br />\n至於&quot;你又知唔係淘寶用外國shop既圖？&quot;呢個問題 <br />\n其實你上淘寶去男裝度睇其實會成日都見到果個model <br />\n我諗應該無公司會比個model接咁多唔同既牌子 <br />\n例如 Off white ,White mountaineering ,Thrasher <br />\n當然係真係假 大家都係明眼人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f953a71636288b47f5c42c666754de9062ea529","tid":115741,"uid":52516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>賣300蚊條褲有閪錢告誹謗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同果啲笑人賣魚蛋冇錢買樓既人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果每樣賣貴三倍 一百賺二百<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都搵唔少油水下</blockquote><br />\n你講到好似每日都好撚好生意咁<br />\n日日有客咩<br />\n咁易係人都做啦<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得賣淘寶貨無問題<br />\n問題係在於唔好標榜自己 又美國 又台灣入貨 又歐洲入貨</blockquote><br />\n我無鬧過佢地咁樣做生意 佢地明買明賣無錯 <br />\n只係提醒下唔知道既人 <br />\n如果粗略估計 其實佢地都搵得唔少 <span style=\"color: red;\">以下都係假設</span><br />\n一件原價90蚊左右o既衫佢地賣$299 約賺$200蚊<br />\n一條原價120蚊左右o既褲佢地賣$360 約賺$240蚊<br />\n一個月衫褲各賣一百件（最小估計 未計可能直接同廠拎成本更低 實際賣出件數應該更多）<br />\n生意少既月份約月入$40000 減去貨倉成本$10000（Fb贊助費無法估計）佢地係網店既收入可能已經有$30000 生意好自然賺得更多 <br />\n以上都係假設同討論 如果有錯歡迎指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b96249b4a281450332dad33b6234702daa8d3c1","tid":115741,"uid":67210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"之前fb都見過一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/11/130733_1dcb3e3c00fd1f7ca0f559ae731600ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F11%2F130733_1dcb3e3c00fd1f7ca0f559ae731600ef.jpg&h=0260818f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4a63d5fb2adca89cb67dbaee0752edc5a86e512","tid":115741,"uid":49109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"肥閪開倉大把貨都淘番嚟。人地$10一塊mon貼，佢單價賣$50"},{"pid":"4c7a935cffa88cf77887bcaf821a2b9ee47d66c4","tid":115741,"uid":37329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f58e1e48fd92a9a469a0d371c7a9572815f00ad","tid":115741,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>賣300蚊條褲有閪錢告誹謗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同果啲笑人賣魚蛋冇錢買樓既人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果每樣賣貴三倍 一百賺二百<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都搵唔少油水下</blockquote><br />\n你講到好似每日都好撚好生意咁<br />\n日日有客咩<br />\n咁易係人都做啦<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得賣淘寶貨無問題<br />\n問題係在於唔好標榜自己 又美國 又台灣入貨 又歐洲入貨</blockquote><br />\n我無鬧過佢地咁樣做生意 佢地明買明賣無錯 <br />\n只係提醒下唔知道既人 <br />\n如果粗略估計 其實佢地都搵得唔少 <span style=\"color: red;\">以下都係假設</span><br />\n一件原價90蚊左右o既衫佢地賣$299 約賺$200蚊<br />\n一條原價120蚊左右o既褲佢地賣$360 約賺$240蚊<br />\n一個月衫褲各賣一百件（最小估計 未計可能直接同廠拎成本更低 實際賣出件數應該更多）<br />\n生意少既月份約月入$40000 減去貨倉成本$10000（Fb贊助費無法估計）佢地係網店既收入可能已經有$30000 生意好自然賺得更多 <br />\n以上都係假設同討論 如果有錯歡迎指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有二百件咁多 我諗一日最多咪兩三單<br />\n一個月最多咪一百單"},{"pid":"cb670031bfe59bae8498677e52fbb71ccacbaa47","tid":115741,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T10:00:16.000Z","msg":"其實而家網店都好飽和下<br />\n特別淘寶既出現<br />\n<br />\nIg shop生意無你想像中咁好<br />\n除左second kill d 老字號"},{"pid":"add63d7a7973f072b43c6a09270f679823a588c5","tid":115741,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"其實有啲淘寶相係偷，我有朋友自己影左啲衫既相（佢自己去韓國入貨既）都俾淘寶偷左相放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以巴打話偷圖 未必錯晒"},{"pid":"906c0227717ee936527ac0d29b44a1b5d2a78415","tid":115741,"uid":26220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽講好似話淘寶d相係外國網抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後淘寶店搵廠整條一模一樣<br />\n不過fb 果d係咪賣緊淘寶貨就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oG0XMd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oG0XMd.jpg&h=8baba264&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43cAD13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43cAD13.jpg&h=b024a194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連個model 都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我都幾肯定係淘寶貨 因為呢個鬼仔都幫好多唔同樣既淘寶衫做model 假如假off white <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩叫假如假off white<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如假off white</span> 打錯字對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6y083T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail